{"about_the_game":"\u300aGeometry Raid\u300bis a rogue-lite space slash shooter game, the game combines classic barrage shooting and sword slash game elements. By driving a two-part ship,you can shoot and swing tail  to crush the enemy . The game focuses on hardcore physics simulation and maximizing the melee slash experience.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2>Hardcore 2D sword melee slash simulation and the multiple genres built around it<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2766600/extras/GIF_small_1.gif?t=1739324457\" /><br>Hardcore physics collision simulation: The movement of players, enemies, and bullets is simulated by the Godot physics engine to create a realistic sense of impact<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2766600/extras/GIF_small_6.gif?t=1739324457\" /><br>Hardcore damage calculation: Inspired by the damage system of riding and slashing, which I incorporated into my game, in-game damage is determined by factors such as quality and relative speed. This means that the faster the relative velocity between objects, the higher the damage caused<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2766600/extras/GIF_small_3.gif?t=1739324457\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2766600/extras/GIF_small_4.gif?t=1739324457\" /><br>Geometry Madness is a game in continuous development, and I will be updating it constantly to expand the depth and content of the game.","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2766600?t=1739324457","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2766600?t=1739324457","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2766600/capsule_231x87_alt_assets_0.jpg?t=1739324457","capsule_imagev5":"h